Operation Text: SELECT      trim(CDTABLA) as CDTABLA,     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS CDELEMEN,     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSELEMEN     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET WHERE trim(CDTABLA) = 'KTOTVMG'  AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'

select a.* from ( SELECT      trim(CDTABLA) as CDTABLA,     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS CDELEMEN,     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSELEMEN     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET WHERE TRIM(CDELEMEN) = '0004'  AND CDIDIOMA ='ES' ) a inner join ( SELECT      trim(CDTABLA) as CDTABLA,     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS CDELEMEN,     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSELEMEN     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET WHERE TRIM(CDELEMEN) = '0034'  AND CDIDIOMA ='ES' ) b on (a.CDTABLA = b.CDTABLA) inner join ( SELECT      trim(CDTABLA) as CDTABLA,     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS CDELEMEN,     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSELEMEN     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET WHERE TRIM(CDELEMEN) = '0020'  AND CDIDIOMA ='ES' ) c on (a.CDTABLA = c.CDTABLA) inner join ( SELECT      trim(CDTABLA) as CDTABLA,     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS CDELEMEN,     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSELEMEN     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET WHERE TRIM(CDELEMEN) = '0002'  AND CDIDIOMA ='ES' ) d on (a.CDTABLA = d.CDTABLA)

SELECT tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdnumpol,tbl_tmp_kcim23t.ctvrspol,tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdprodte,tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdprodco,
     
       CASE WHEN  join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdelem ='CPASEGUR' AND join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.nocampfi IN ('IMCAMP03','IMCAMP04','IMCAMP05') 
           THEN tbl_tmp_kcim23t.imcamp03
           ELSE NULL
           END AS cpasegur,
           
       CASE WHEN  join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdelem ='CDOPCLIQ' AND join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.nocampfi IN ('TXCAMP01','TXCAMP02','TXCAMP10','TXCAMP46') 
           THEN ''
           ELSE ''
           END AS cdopcliq
         
     FROM
         (
         SELECT u.cdnumpol, u.ctvrspol, u.cdprodte, u.cdprodco, u.imcamp03, u.nurelrem, u.cdmct 
             FROM (
                   SELECT polver.cdnumpol, polver.ctvrspol, k23t.nurelrem, TRIM(k23t.cdprodte) AS cdprodte, TRIM(k23t.cdprodco) AS cdprodco,
     			   MAX(k23t.imcamp03) AS imcamp03, k23t.cdmct, k23t.cdobjtp, k23t.ctsecobj,
                    ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY  polver.cdnumpol ORDER BY  polver.ctvrspol DESC) AS orden
                   
                    FROM bddlcru.kcim23t k23t 
                    INNER JOIN bddltrn.adc_t_inf_uni_poliza_version polver ON k23t.cdnumpol=polver.cdnumpol AND k23t.ctvrspol=polver.ctvrspol 
                       WHERE k23t.nurelrem=1 
                       GROUP BY  polver.cdnumpol,  polver.ctvrspol, k23t.nurelrem, k23t.cdprodte, k23t.cdprodco, k23t.cdmct, k23t.cdobjtp, k23t.ctsecobj
             ) AS u 
                  WHERE u.orden = 1
     
         ) AS tbl_tmp_kcim23t 
     	 LEFT OUTER JOIN
         (
         SELECT DISTINCT tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdprodte,tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdprodco,tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdelem,TRIM(ktpm04t.dselemtp) AS dselemtp,
             tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.nocampfi,tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.nurerelc AS nurelrem,tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdmct 
             FROM (
                 SELECT DISTINCT TRIM(ktpa82t.cdprodte) AS cdprodte, TRIM(ktpa82t.cdprodco) AS cdprodco, ktpa82t.cdobjtp, TRIM(ktpa82t.cdelem) AS cdelem,
                 ktpa82t.nurerelc, TRIM(ktpa82t.nocampfi) AS nocampfi, ktpa82t.cdmcr, ktpa82t.cdmct FROM bddlcru.ktpa82t AS ktpa82t 
                 
                   WHERE ktpa82t.nurerelc <> 0 AND ktpa82t.cdmct <> '0000000000' AND ktpa82t.cdmcr = '0000000000' AND 
                         (TRIM(cdelem) = 'CPASEGUR' OR TRIM(cdelem) = 'CDOPCLIQ') 
                 
                 ) AS tbl_tmp_ktpa82t INNER JOIN 
                 
                 bddlcru.ktpm04t ON TRIM(ktpm04t.cdelem)=tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdelem 
                     WHERE tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdelem IS NOT NULL
                 
         ) AS join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t ON
         
             tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdprodte=join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdprodte AND tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdprodco=join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdprodco 
             AND tbl_tmp_kcim23t.nurelrem=join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.nurelrem AND tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdmct=join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdmct

SELECT tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdnumpol,tbl_tmp_kcim23t.ctvrspol,tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdprodte,tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdprodco,
     
       CASE WHEN  join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdelem ='CPASEGUR' AND join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.nocampfi IN ('IMCAMP03','IMCAMP04','IMCAMP05') 
           THEN tbl_tmp_kcim23t.imcamp03
           ELSE NULL
           END AS cpasegur,
           
       CASE WHEN  join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdelem ='CDOPCLIQ' AND join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.nocampfi IN ('TXCAMP01','TXCAMP02','TXCAMP10','TXCAMP46') 
           THEN ''
           ELSE ''
           END AS cdopcliq
         
     FROM
         (
         SELECT u.cdnumpol, u.ctvrspol, u.cdprodte, u.cdprodco, u.imcamp03, u.nurelrem, u.cdmct 
             FROM (
                   SELECT polver.cdnumpol, polver.ctvrspol, k23t.nurelrem, TRIM(k23t.cdprodte) AS cdprodte, TRIM(k23t.cdprodco) AS cdprodco,
     			   MAX(k23t.imcamp03) AS imcamp03, k23t.cdmct, k23t.cdobjtp, k23t.ctsecobj,
                    ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY  polver.cdnumpol ORDER BY  polver.ctvrspol DESC) AS orden
                   
                    FROM bddlcru.kcim23t k23t 
                    INNER JOIN bddltrn.adc_t_inf_uni_poliza_version polver ON k23t.cdnumpol=polver.cdnumpol AND k23t.ctvrspol=polver.ctvrspol 
                       WHERE k23t.nurelrem=1 
                       GROUP BY  polver.cdnumpol,  polver.ctvrspol, k23t.nurelrem, k23t.cdprodte, k23t.cdprodco, k23t.cdmct, k23t.cdobjtp, k23t.ctsecobj
             ) AS u 
                  WHERE u.orden = 1
     
         ) AS tbl_tmp_kcim23t 
     	 LEFT OUTER JOIN
         (
         SELECT DISTINCT tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdprodte,tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdprodco,tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdelem,TRIM(ktpm04t.dselemtp) AS dselemtp,
             tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.nocampfi,tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.nurerelc AS nurelrem,tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdmct 
             FROM (
                 SELECT DISTINCT TRIM(ktpa82t.cdprodte) AS cdprodte, TRIM(ktpa82t.cdprodco) AS cdprodco, ktpa82t.cdobjtp, TRIM(ktpa82t.cdelem) AS cdelem,
                 ktpa82t.nurerelc, TRIM(ktpa82t.nocampfi) AS nocampfi, ktpa82t.cdmcr, ktpa82t.cdmct FROM bddlcru.ktpa82t AS ktpa82t 
                 
                   WHERE ktpa82t.nurerelc <> 0 AND ktpa82t.cdmct <> '0000000000' AND ktpa82t.cdmcr = '0000000000' AND 
                         (TRIM(cdelem) = 'CPASEGUR' OR TRIM(cdelem) = 'CDOPCLIQ') 
                 
                 ) AS tbl_tmp_ktpa82t INNER JOIN 
                 
                 bddlcru.ktpm04t ON TRIM(ktpm04t.cdelem)=tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdelem 
                     WHERE tbl_tmp_ktpa82t.cdelem IS NOT NULL
                 
         ) AS join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t ON
         
             tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdprodte=join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdprodte AND tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdprodco=join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdprodco 
             AND tbl_tmp_kcim23t.nurelrem=join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.nurelrem AND tbl_tmp_kcim23t.cdmct=join_ktpa82t_ktpm04t.cdmct

select count(1),CLPROTI from (  SELECT                                               CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL, CDOBJTP, CTSECOBJ,FECONTAB,FECAMBIO,CDCIAGRU,CDNUMREC, INRECIFR, INDEMIAN,NUAPUNTE,FEPROMEC,CDINTERC,TCCDMONE,FECMVTO,TCDOMORI,NUSECMVO,NUTRAB,FECTRAB,                                               CDPRODTE, CDPRODCO, CDESTRUP, CDRAMDGS, TCTINEGO, CDMEDPAG, INFISMOR, CLPROTI, CLPROUN, CDESTRUG, CLGESTI,CLGESUN,                                               CLFILTOM, CDFILPAG,TCTITXCT,CONCAT(TCTITXCT,TCCOPERA) AS CDOPERA, CDMCT, TCCOPERA,                                               IMPCEC01 AS IMPRNTEC,                                  /* PRIMA TECNICA */                                               IMPCEC18 AS IMPCOBRC,                                  /* IMPORTE COMISION BRUTA C*/                                               IMPCEC09 AS DESCCOME,                                  /* DESC. COMERCIAL */                                               IMPCEC03 + IMPCEC07 AS IMREPAFR,                       /* IMP. RECARGOS (PAGO FRACCIONADO Y DESC POR DOMICILIACION) */                                               IMPCEC04 AS IMDERECH,                                  /* DERECHOS */                                               IMPCEC05 AS IMIVAPRN,                                  /* IVA SOBRE PRIMA NETA */                                               IMPCEC06 AS IMIVADER,                                  /* IVA SOBRE DERECHOS */                                               IMPCEC10 AS IMGGINEX,                                  /* GASTOS DE GESTION INTERNA Y EXTERNA */                                               IMPCEC02 AS IMCESCOM,                                  /* CESION DE COMISION */                                               IMPCEC19 AS IMPRNETA,                                  /* PRIMA NETA */                                               IMPCEC20 AS IMPRITOT,                                  /* PRIMA TOTAL */                                               tsultmod,                                               'INFO' AS SISTORIG                                          FROM  bddltrn.ktom41  T                              --- MEC SEGURO DIRECTO                                          WHERE  CDCIAGRU = 'AU'                      /* CODIGO COMPANIA GRUPO */                                                AND TCTITXCT IN ('001','003')              /* TC TIPO TRANSACCION CONTABLE */                                                AND TCCOPERA IN ('004','005')  )X group by CLPROTI

select count(1),CLFILTOM from (  SELECT                                               CDNUMPOL, CTVRSPOL, CDOBJTP, CTSECOBJ,FECONTAB,FECAMBIO,CDCIAGRU,CDNUMREC, INRECIFR, INDEMIAN,NUAPUNTE,FEPROMEC,CDINTERC,TCCDMONE,FECMVTO,TCDOMORI,NUSECMVO,NUTRAB,FECTRAB,                                               CDPRODTE, CDPRODCO, CDESTRUP, CDRAMDGS, TCTINEGO, CDMEDPAG, INFISMOR, CLPROTI, CLPROUN, CDESTRUG, CLGESTI,CLGESUN,                                               CLFILTOM, CDFILPAG,TCTITXCT,CONCAT(TCTITXCT,TCCOPERA) AS CDOPERA, CDMCT, TCCOPERA,                                               IMPCEC01 AS IMPRNTEC,                                  /* PRIMA TECNICA */                                               IMPCEC18 AS IMPCOBRC,                                  /* IMPORTE COMISION BRUTA C*/                                               IMPCEC09 AS DESCCOME,                                  /* DESC. COMERCIAL */                                               IMPCEC03 + IMPCEC07 AS IMREPAFR,                       /* IMP. RECARGOS (PAGO FRACCIONADO Y DESC POR DOMICILIACION) */                                               IMPCEC04 AS IMDERECH,                                  /* DERECHOS */                                               IMPCEC05 AS IMIVAPRN,                                  /* IVA SOBRE PRIMA NETA */                                               IMPCEC06 AS IMIVADER,                                  /* IVA SOBRE DERECHOS */                                               IMPCEC10 AS IMGGINEX,                                  /* GASTOS DE GESTION INTERNA Y EXTERNA */                                               IMPCEC02 AS IMCESCOM,                                  /* CESION DE COMISION */                                               IMPCEC19 AS IMPRNETA,                                  /* PRIMA NETA */                                               IMPCEC20 AS IMPRITOT,                                  /* PRIMA TOTAL */                                               tsultmod,                                               'INFO' AS SISTORIG                                          FROM  bddltrn.ktom41  T                              --- MEC SEGURO DIRECTO                                          WHERE  CDCIAGRU = 'AU'                      /* CODIGO COMPANIA GRUPO */                                                AND TCTITXCT IN ('001','003')              /* TC TIPO TRANSACCION CONTABLE */                                                AND TCCOPERA IN ('004','005')  )X group by CLFILTOM

SELECT CAST(`au_restec_hist`.`anio_comp` AS STRING) AS `anio_comp`,   `au_restec_hist`.`canal` AS `canal`,   SUM(`au_restec_hist`.`priemi`) AS `sum_priemi_ok` FROM `bddldes`.`au_restec_hist` `au_restec_hist` WHERE ((`au_restec_hist`.`canal` IN ('Agentes', 'Despachos y Corredores', 'Masivos')) AND ((CASE WHEN (`au_restec_hist`.`id_cluster` = 'X') THEN 'SI' ELSE 'NO' END) IN ('NO', 'SI')) AND (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` NOT IN ('TRANSPORTE DE CARGA')) AND (`au_restec_hist`.`dmes` NOT IN ('Diciembre', 'Noviembre', 'Octubre'))) GROUP BY 1,   2
SELECT `au_restec_hist`.`tipo_pro` AS `tipo_pro` FROM `bddldes`.`au_restec_hist` `au_restec_hist` GROUP BY 1 LIMIT 48
SELECT `au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` AS `dgrupo2` FROM `bddldes`.`au_restec_hist` `au_restec_hist` GROUP BY 1 LIMIT 32

SELECT (CASE WHEN ((`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'ADMON ESPECIAL') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'AUTOMOVILES') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'DECLARACIONES') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'FRONTERIZOS AUTO') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'MOTOCICLETAS') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'P. DE PASAJEROS AUT') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'PLAN PISO') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'SIN DATOS') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'TURISTAS')) THEN 'RESIDENTES' WHEN ((`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'CAMIONES') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'P. DE PASAJEROS BUS') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'REMOLQUES') OR (`au_restec_hist`.`dgrupo2` = 'TRACTOCAMIONES')) THEN 'EQUIPO PESADO' ELSE 'PICK UPS' END) AS `calculation_4047047265015230472`,   SUM(`au_restec_hist`.`priemi`) AS `temp_tc___3703150471__0_`,   CAST(`au_restec_hist`.`anio_comp` AS STRING) AS `anio_comp` FROM `bddldes`.`au_restec_hist` `au_restec_hist` WHERE (`au_restec_hist`.`dmes` IN ('Abril', 'Agosto', 'Enero', 'Febrero', 'Julio', 'Junio', 'Marzo', 'Mayo', 'Septiembre')) GROUP BY 1,   3
SELECT CAST(`au_restec_hist`.`anio_comp` AS STRING) AS `anio_comp` FROM `bddldes`.`au_restec_hist` `au_restec_hist` GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY CAST(`au_restec_hist`.`anio_comp` AS STRING) ASC NULLS FIRST
SELECT `au_restec_hist`.`dmes` AS `dmes` FROM `bddldes`.`au_restec_hist` `au_restec_hist` GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY `au_restec_hist`.`dmes` ASC NULLS FIRST
